{"name": "django-session-switcher", "metadata": {"name": "django-session-switcher", "version": "0.2.1", "classifiers": ["Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Django", "Framework :: Django :: 5.0", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: BSD License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3 :: Only", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP :: Dynamic Content"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["django"], "summary": "A Django app to quickly switch between django users.", "upload_time": 1735260226}, "documentation": ["# django-session-switcher\n\ndjango-session-switcher allows you to quickly switch between dummy users. Handy tool to\ncreate dummy content for your side projects from multiple users.\n\n## Usage\n\n\n1. Install the package\n```\npip install django-session-switcher\n```\n\n2. Add `django_session_switcher` to your `INSTALLED_APPS` settings.\n\n```\nINSTALLED_APPS = [\n    ...,\n    \"django_session_switcher\",\n]\n```\n\n3. Add the middleware to your project\n\n```\nMIDDLEWARE = [\n    ...,\n    \"django_session_switcher.middleware.SessionSwitcherMiddleware\",\n]\n```\n\n4. Include the django_session_switchers URLconf in your project urls.py like this\n\n```\npath(\"__dss__/\", include(\"django_session_switcher.urls\")),\n```\n\n5. Run `python manage.py migrate` to create the models.\n\n6. You need to add the dummy users to the django_session_switcher's `Session User` model. You\n   can do this through django admin.\n\n7. Once you have added some users to `Session User` you will be able to switch between\n   added users with a single click.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "django_session_switcher.migrations", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher.migrations.0001_initial", "documentation": ["Generated by Django 5.1.2 on 2024-11-09 21:56"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "django_session_switcher.migrations.0001_initial.Migration", "bases": ["migrations.Migration"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "django_session_switcher.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.initial", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.dependencies", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher.migrations.0001_initial.Migration.operations", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher.admin", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "django_session_switcher.admin.SessionUserAdmin", "bases": ["admin.ModelAdmin"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "django_session_switcher.admin.SessionUserAdmin.fields", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher.admin.SessionUserAdmin.list_display", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher.admin.SessionUserAdmin.search_fields", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher.views", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "django_session_switcher.views.switch_user", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "request", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "django_session_switcher.apps", "documentation": [], "functions": 